  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GRAP UR GUN AND EMBARK ON ENDLESS ADVENTURE! </h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521250/extras/9458af4f09cbbab8df5d26989b5d719f.poster.avif?t=1717544455\" width=600 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521250/extras/9458af4f09cbbab8df5d26989b5d719f.webm?t=1717544455\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521250/extras/9458af4f09cbbab8df5d26989b5d719f.mp4?t=1717544455\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Penguru is a hack and slash game where you play as an angry Penguin. Wreak havoc upon your foes as either a Penguin Ninja or a Penguru Terminator! Penguru has un-ending action, eye satisfaction of cool pixel art and hilarious dark humor.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHOOUSE UR BATTLESTYLE!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521250/extras/4b0e6a2a5ecef60d30abc01e2993d737.poster.avif?t=1717544455\" width=600 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521250/extras/4b0e6a2a5ecef60d30abc01e2993d737.webm?t=1717544455\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521250/extras/4b0e6a2a5ecef60d30abc01e2993d737.mp4?t=1717544455\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Choose your weapon, shoot, blow, cut and rip your way through waves of enemies. Do you have what it takes to avenge your Penguin and deliver him the title of Penguru?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DESTROY THE KINGS OF THE OCEAN!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521250/extras/d16c858f999c3c0c6ddb80f0d97276b5.poster.avif?t=1717544455\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521250/extras/d16c858f999c3c0c6ddb80f0d97276b5.webm?t=1717544455\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521250/extras/d16c858f999c3c0c6ddb80f0d97276b5.mp4?t=1717544455\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Get your mission! Battle against bosses you chose. Challenge wild life into a test of gunpowder, steel and blood.",
