eam/apps/2521250/extras/d16c858f999c3c0c6ddb80f0d97276b5.poster.avif?t=1717544455\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521250/extras/d16c858f999c3c0c6ddb80f0d97276b5.webm?t=1717544455\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2521250/extras/d16c858f999c3c0c6ddb80f0d97276b5.mp4?t=1717544455\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Get your mission! Battle against bosses you chose. Challenge wild life into a test of gunpowder, steel and blood.",
